        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "The HTM securities net carrying amounts at March 31, 2026 and December 31, 2025 reflect an ACL of $62 million and $60 million, respectively, predominantly related to Non-agency CMBS. See Note 2 in the 2025 Form 10-K for a description of the ACL methodology used for HTM Securities.",
